title: Smoky Chorizo & King Prawn Rice Three Steps | Ready in 10
description: Little can beat the smell of sizzling chorizo. Well, apart from the taste! Combined with the delicate flavour prawns, the two are a match made in foodie heaven. Seasoned with Mexican spice for a welcome kick of heat, this super-speedy dish is easy to make and even easier to enjoy.
